All Versions

  • Compare Networks: Export - Added all providers types to Overlap By Network Details section
  • Assess Markets: Added Include Market Leaders checkbox for option to include Market Leaders in report or not
  • Rank Networks: Fixed"Network has already been excluded" error when double-clicking to remove a network from Ranking Details tab
  • Provider Profile: Granted permission to all user to view CMS tab
  • Release Notes: Moved to Help page
  • Manage Clients: Moved tile from Home page to Settings page
  • Users: Renamed to Manage Users
  • Tags: Moved Tags to Settings page
